$hr
Download:${downspeed enp0s31f6}${goto 190}Upload:${upspeed enp0s31f6}
${downspeedgraph enp0s31f6 50,180 000000 ffffff} ${upspeedgraph enp0s31f6 50,180 000000 ffffff}
